# Intuit Design System - Opacity Token Library

## Primitive Opacity Tokens (DO NOT USE DIRECTLY IN PLUGINS)

- `--opacity-0`: 0
- `--opacity-5`: 0.05
- `--opacity-10`: 0.1
- `--opacity-15`: 0.15
- `--opacity-20`: 0.2
- `--opacity-30`: 0.3
- `--opacity-33`: 0.33
- `--opacity-40`: 0.4
- `--opacity-50`: 0.5
- `--opacity-60`: 0.6
- `--opacity-70`: 0.7
- `--opacity-80`: 0.8
- `--opacity-90`: 0.9
- `--opacity-100`: 1

## Semantic Opacity Tokens (USE THESE IN PLUGINS)

### Disabled
- `--opacity-disabled`: --opacity-50 /* For use when a component needs to be displayed disabled to set its opacity lighter */

### Shadow
- `--opacity-shadow`: --opacity-20 /* For use when a shadow needs an opacity */
